profile.title: Some information about me
profile.text1: My name is Le Anh Duc. I am a 2001 student with many dreams and aspirations since childhood. But unfortunately most of those dreams have yet to come true. I am currently a student majoring in Information Technology at the Academy of Cryptography Techniques.
profile.timeline-content: I was born on February 5, 2001 in Nghe An. Born and raised here, now that I'm far away, I miss my hometown so much  In 2019, I graduated at Nguyen Duy Trinh High School and also started living away from  home to pursue college dreams from here.
